Scripture Data Attribution
==========================

Greek Text: Textus Receptus (Scrivener 1894)
License: Public Domain

Morphological Tagging & Lexical Data:
Source: STEP Bible (https://www.stepbible.org)
License: CC BY 4.0 (https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/)
Original Data: Tyndale House, Cambridge

HuggingFace Dataset:
URL: https://huggingface.co/datasets/hmcgovern/original-language-bibles-greek
Curator: Hope McGovern

Upstream Repository:
URL: https://github.com/STEPBible/STEPBible-Data

This package extracts only Textus Receptus readings (manuscript_source containing 'K')
from the TAGNT dataset to ensure use of only public domain Greek text.
